            <h3>index</h3>
            <p>index is a sequentially numbered integer starting from 0, with 0 being the farthest back and higher values being the farthest forward. The index cannot be a negative value or a number greater than the current highest index plus one.</p>

            <h3>addChild</h3>
            <p>addChild method adds a DisplayObject to the foremost position in the DisplayObjectContainer.</p>
            <p class="tutorial-image"><img src="<%= path %>assets/img/tutorial/addChild.svg" alt="addChild"></p>

            <h5>Example</h5>
            <p><pre>const {Shape} = next2d.display;
const shape = new Shape();
shape
    .graphics
    .beginFill()
    .drawCircle(0, 0, 100);
const root = next2d.createRootMovieClip();
this.addChild(shape);</pre></p>

            <h3>addChildAt</h3>
            <p>addChildAt method adds a DisplayObject to the specified index position in the DisplayObjectContainer.</p>
            <p class="tutorial-image"><img src="<%= path %>assets/img/tutorial/addChildAt.svg" alt="addChildAt"></p>

            <h5>Example</h5>
            <p><pre>const {Shape} = next2d.display;
const shape = new Shape();
shape
    .graphics
    .beginFill()
    .drawCircle(0, 0, 100);
this.addChildAt(shape, 0);</pre></p>

            <h3>removeChild, removeChildAt</h3>
            <p>removeChild and removeChildAt methods remove the specified DisplayObject from the DisplayObjectContainer. If there are any DisplayObjects after the removed index, they will be relocated to a smaller index position (back).</p>
            <p class="tutorial-image"><img src="<%= path %>assets/img/tutorial/removeChild.svg" alt="addChildAt"></p>

            <h5>Example</h5>
            <p><pre>const {Shape} = next2d.display;
const shape = new Shape();
shape
    .graphics
    .beginFill()
    .drawCircle(0, 0, 100);
this.addChildAt(shape, 1);
this.removeChild(shape);
</pre></p>

            <p><pre>const {Shape} = next2d.display;
const shape = new Shape();
shape
    .graphics
    .beginFill()
    .drawCircle(0, 0, 100);
this.addChildAt(shape, 1);
this.removeChildAt(1);
</pre></p>


